milestones.description: Ashish Bagai has become the top scorer for CAN in ODIs with 567 runs, going past John Davison's 457
Hamilton has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Majid Haq's record
Ashish Bagai's 137 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for CAN), surpassing John Davison's 111
Ashish Bagai and Ashif Mulla's 100-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 86 between Ian Billcliff and Joe Harris
Hamilton and Fraser Watts's 56-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 45 between Hamilton and Fraser Watts
Ryan Watson has broken the record for most catches (5) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Ian Philip's 4
Ashish Bagai and Ashif Mulla's 100-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Ishwar Maraj and John Davison
